Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.20,0:00:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愛妳 愛到出神陶醉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.34,0:00:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愛妳 愛到懊惱萬分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.21,0:00:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼也不怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.62,0:00:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愛妳 無法忘記妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.79,0:00:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,風兒硬是拆開\N我們纏綿甜蜜的吻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.97,0:00:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,面對無法停止的熾熱心動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.21,0:00:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請不要流淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.11,0:00:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,令人無法討厭的冷漠態度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.35,0:00:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,見不到面令我痛苦萬分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.22,0:01:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳鬱悶不樂的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.42,0:01:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,令我心碎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.19,0:01:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愛妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.47,0:01:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愛妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.54,0:01:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愛妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.60,0:01:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來…了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.64,0:01:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你回來了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.81,0:01:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.94,0:01:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回老家去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.84,0:01:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說她媽媽因為感冒病倒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.01,0:02:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.45,0:02:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這是什麼眼神?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.35,0:02:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是又要催她再婚…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.29,0:02:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然有可能談到這個話題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.36,0:02:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,偶爾總要回去\N孝順父母一下嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.86,0:02:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又不是說一去不回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.03,0:02:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳說得對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.06,0:02:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員該不會\N就這樣一去不回吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.67,0:02:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#48 五代激動的告白!\N請了解我的心!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.98,0:02:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸,背我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.72,0:02:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦,小悅\N爸爸已經很累了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.66,0:02:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會啦,不要緊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.93,0:02:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.46,0:02:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.77,0:02:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒喔,好棒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.84,0:03:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.78,0:03:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,律子,感冒好點了沒?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.68,0:03:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸,你回來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.82,0:03:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響…響子!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.69,0:03:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼來了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.65,0:03:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子,妳怎麼會現在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.12,0:03:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.06,0:03:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這還用問嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.59,0:03:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就如你所見,我是來幫媽媽代打的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.03,0:03:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊,妳來看我們啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.13,0:03:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.20,0:03:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸,你還拿著鞋子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.91,0:03:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個就別管了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.81,0:03:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,老婆,響子來了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.75,0:03:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公,什麼事啊\N跟小孩似的叫得這麼大聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.68,0:03:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子,響子來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.19,0:03:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我叫她來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.45,0:03:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼把鞋子拿到這裡來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.09,0:03:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,因為我太高興了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.30,0:03:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來他們這麼高興啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.11,0:04:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇,真好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.78,0:04:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫響子回來果然是對的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.65,0:04:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近我連爸爸的生活起居\N都無法照顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.09,0:04:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她只要一逞強做事\N馬上就又發燒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.16,0:04:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的蠻嚴重的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.79,0:04:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸,我幫你倒酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.13,0:04:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,不好意思,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.97,0:04:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳來真的幫了我一個大忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.61,0:04:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,兩三天內不會回來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.05,0:04:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是叫人感到寂寞啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.65,0:04:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他好像熄火了一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.62,0:04:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我哪有!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.32,0:05:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是在唸書嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.26,0:05:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算戴著耳機\N旁邊吵的話,還是聽得到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.80,0:05:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,原來你在唸英文啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.67,0:05:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討厭,你這是幹嘛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.28,0:05:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你很難過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.55,0:05:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員不在的時候\N我會好好照顧你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.68,0:05:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇,好體貼喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.39,0:05:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就像管理員一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.89,0:05:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.50,0:05:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,廁所的電燈泡壞了一直沒有換
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.80,0:05:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,漏水也一直沒有修,不是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.73,0:05:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,修理這個\N也是管理員的工作吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.94,0:05:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經摔壞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.84,0:05:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三萬八千圓…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.58,0:05:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,修得好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.41,0:05:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.55,0:05:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個我就沒辦法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.23,0:06:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣,兩三天轉眼就過去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.43,0:06:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽,妳的身體好像好多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.74,0:06:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.34,0:06:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.71,0:06:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得還是沒什麼精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.55,0:06:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.78,0:06:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,好像還是有點發燒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.35,0:06:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘴巴張開給我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.32,0:06:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,扁桃腺還是有點紅腫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.42,0:06:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.72,0:06:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一二,一二…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.34,0:07:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(外出兩三天管理員)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.16,0:07:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過了四、五天\N管理員還是沒有回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.47,0:07:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員到底\N什麼時候才會回來呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.59,0:07:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎,我們去散步吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.88,0:08:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.65,0:08:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一之瀨先生,下班回家啦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.12,0:08:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,今天我是早班
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.59,0:08:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是去接管理員回來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.96,0:08:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是,我只是出來散步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.37,0:08:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣?我們去附近喝一杯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.81,0:08:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思,硬拉著你陪我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.11,0:08:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會,別這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.81,0:08:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員的母親\N病情真的很嚴重嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.48,0:08:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.69,0:08:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼問題嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.29,0:08:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看到你\N就想起自己年輕的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.63,0:09:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也曾經有過偷偷愛慕的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.78,0:09:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所謂牛糞中的一朵花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.25,0:09:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概就是這個意思吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.62,0:09:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,苦學畢業後\N終於在一家小小的公司就職
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.06,0:09:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個人就在那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.17,0:09:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.08,0:09:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光只是看著她\N我就覺得很幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.79,0:09:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還故意找藉口跟她說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.86,0:10:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這種事會聯想到我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.36,0:10:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一天\N在一個小型的宴會上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.71,0:10:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正想趁這個機會\N和她加深我們的感情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.71,0:10:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.72,0:10:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一之瀨先生\N要不要跟我比酒量啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.59,0:10:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,好耶!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.59,0:10:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你也是海量啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.42,0:10:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花枝是比她\N早進公司一年的前輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.16,0:10:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花枝?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.73,0:10:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名字很美吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.50,0:10:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.13,0:10:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是,花枝,既然要比\N要不要來賭個什麼東西?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.20,0:10:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.04,0:10:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果一之瀨先生贏了\N我就嫁給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.74,0:10:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好耶,我們當證人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.41,0:10:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喝到有一方醉倒為止吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.98,0:10:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,酒錢由我來出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.12,0:11:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這時我警覺到\N我絕對不能贏她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.69,0:11:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是為什麼你贏了呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.43,0:11:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結婚之後我才知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.56,0:11:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說花枝是故意裝醉輸給我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.83,0:11:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.87,0:11:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我輸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.04,0:11:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不,是我輸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.24,0:11:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我履行我的承諾\N我願意嫁給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.64,0:11:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不,不用啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.48,0:11:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是陷阱嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.48,0:11:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不,聽說這算是她的求婚方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.75,0:11:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思,再來一杯酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.12,0:11:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.52,0:11:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我個性比較軟弱\N就照著她的話結婚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.49,0:11:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.44,0:11:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,現在我覺得\N我能跟她結婚真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.28,0:12:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.98,0:12:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.12,0:12:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.32,0:12:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.93,0:12:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一之瀨先生\N什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.17,0:12:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你所說牛糞中的一朵花的\N那女生,現在怎麼樣了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.77,0:12:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.91,0:12:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想她一定在某個地方\N過著幸福的生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.51,0:12:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牛糞中的一朵花嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.50,0:12:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,好久沒在廚房吃飯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.31,0:13:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽,妳已經好了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.68,0:13:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我差不多想回一刻館…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.71,0:13:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了,你還記得嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.75,0:13:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子唸高中的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.58,0:13:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,這麼說來的確是她高中的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.72,0:13:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.49,0:13:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,我們經常吃花生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.19,0:13:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我總不能一個禮拜以上\N放著公寓不管啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.57,0:13:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感冒這種病啊\N快要好的時候最重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.00,0:13:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看妳完全好了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.24,0:13:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳這是什麼話\N還得讓她休息兩三天才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.75,0:13:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看看喔,麵包吃了\N牛奶也喝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.45,0:13:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公,時間到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.25,0:13:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對喔,對喔\N時間到了,上班上班
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.22,0:13:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天我會早點回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.39,0:13:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.43,0:13:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,路上小心喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.03,0:13:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,記住喔,絕對不能讓她回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.00,0:14:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盡量把一家團圓的\N歡樂時間拉長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.60,0:14:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一旦讓她走了\N下次不曉得什麼時候才會來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.77,0:14:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要讓她逃掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.11,0:14:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們在說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.34,0:14:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.68,0:14:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的得早點回一刻館才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.99,0:14:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟我是管理員\N我有責任在身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.42,0:14:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的有事的話\N他們會打電話來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.13,0:14:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼連絡都沒有啊\N表示還不要緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.63,0:14:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是,妳說只要兩三天\N我沒帶什麼換洗衣服來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.77,0:14:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去買就好了啊,我給妳錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.31,0:14:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要呢,太浪費錢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.98,0:14:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳也要稍微替妳爸爸想想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.49,0:15:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟妳爸爸不是為了\N要妳辭去管理員的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.46,0:15:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者叫妳脫離音無家\N或者叫妳再婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.60,0:15:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是為了這些事情\N才把妳留在家裡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.20,0:15:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們有說過這種事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.94,0:15:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們只是想享受一下\N一家團圓的喜樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.61,0:15:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.51,0:15:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經享受一個禮拜以上了\N不是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.65,0:15:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳就這麼想回去嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.25,0:15:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開開心心的讓我回去啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.06,0:15:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再說…再說,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.76,0:15:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.83,0:15:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,枕頭換了我就睡不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.70,0:15:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,枕頭?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.63,0:15:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.87,0:15:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要一刻館的那個枕頭才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.84,0:15:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊,原來是因為枕頭啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.94,0:15:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,枕頭啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.35,0:15:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暫停一下喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.48,0:15:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了,來了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.18,0:15:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,這裡是一刻館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.65,0:16:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員的媽媽?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.46,0:16:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?枕頭嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.69,0:16:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對,就是枕頭\N響子說一定要那個枕頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.66,0:16:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.56,0:16:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.80,0:16:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.70,0:16:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管…管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.34,0:16:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會,怎麼會無聊呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.04,0:16:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正我閒閒沒事幹\N馬上幫妳送過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.64,0:16:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?等…等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.41,0:16:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪裡啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.35,0:16:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很煩耶\N我有很重要的事要辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.15,0:16:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.52,0:16:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.22,0:16:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她真的叫你送這個去嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.39,0:16:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,管理員她媽媽\N叫我送這個枕頭去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.24,0:16:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個由我來送
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.47,0:16:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.74,0:16:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交給五代的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.77,0:16:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你會聞枕頭的味道\N還會把臉頰貼在枕頭上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.81,0:16:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣枕頭會變臭的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.81,0:16:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真噁心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.28,0:16:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不會呢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.55,0:17:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我給你杯麵啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.82,0:17:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想吃豬排飯耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.52,0:17:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.36,0:17:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一言為定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.39,0:17:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之,只要有了這個\N我就能見到響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.88,0:17:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我出門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.61,0:17:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙在想什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.61,0:17:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是抱著相親的心情去的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.38,0:17:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿著西裝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.12,0:17:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人要衣裝佛要金裝,草枕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.19,0:17:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只為見到心愛的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.36,0:18:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.66,0:18:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我記得你是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.67,0:18:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.64,0:18:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,我想起來了\N以前見過的那個學生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.08,0:18:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸,你回來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.78,0:18:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.78,0:18:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.28,0:18:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五…五代?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.22,0:18:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊,特地送響子的枕頭來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.29,0:18:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,百忙之中,真的很不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.16,0:18:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼,別這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.39,0:18:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼拘束,放輕鬆點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.20,0:18:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.80,0:19:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.04,0:19:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.55,0:19:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,他是怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.42,0:19:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼穿得西裝筆挺的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.19,0:19:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同學,你唸大幾了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.72,0:19:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是,我叫五代\N接下來要升大四了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.99,0:19:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼馬上就要準備就業了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.96,0:19:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.63,0:19:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,你想去哪裡工作呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.47,0:19:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛,還沒有具體的目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.50,0:19:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.77,0:19:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行,這種事要說清楚一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.68,0:19:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想進入一流貿易公司工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.88,0:19:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,你唸哪一所大學?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.19,0:19:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣太失禮了吧\N好像在做身家調查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.66,0:19:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,對不起喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.72,0:19:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.39,0:20:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我唸的大學\N並不是丟臉到難以回答吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.33,0:20:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天真的很感謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.47,0:20:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來,響子似乎就願意\N暫時住在這裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.64,0:20:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.47,0:20:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒說過這種話吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.64,0:20:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只說枕頭不對\N想回一刻館去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.71,0:20:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這位同學,你有女朋友吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.33,0:20:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒有女朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.70,0:20:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是有喜歡的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.47,0:20:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是單戀嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.40,0:20:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,這個啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.27,0:20:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對方是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.71,0:20:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽,不要問人家這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.48,0:20:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.28,0:20:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個女生,有一頭長髪\N個性溫柔體貼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.19,0:21:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.39,0:21:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她比我大兩歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.86,0:21:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得她很可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.73,0:21:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說才好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.20,0:21:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,大你兩歲啊?\N那她有在工作嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.93,0:21:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.70,0:21:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要再問了,太失禮了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.31,0:21:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會嗎?我不覺得失禮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.11,0:21:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟是年輕人嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.31,0:21:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是從事什麼職業的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.08,0:21:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.75,0:21:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個人是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.58,0:21:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.37,0:21:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從…從事管理工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.77,0:21:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理工作?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.44,0:21:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.28,0:21:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代\N是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.24,0:22:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綜合你剛才講的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.65,0:22:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡的那個人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.89,0:22:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.86,0:22:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡的那個人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.20,0:22:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很了不起啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.50,0:22:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.07,0:22:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是既然對方那麼了不起\N你也得好好加油才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.05,0:22:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,你們說得對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.87,0:22:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子能明白我的心意嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.17,0:22:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該會明白吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.71,0:23:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子在幹什麼啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.81,0:23:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.02,0:23:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來她真的很喜歡那個枕頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.32,0:23:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她喜歡就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.66,0:23:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正她還會留在家裡\N陪我們一陣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.89,0:23:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請不要這樣嚇我,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.06,0:23:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你突然…突然說出那種話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.73,0:23:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫我怎麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.48,0:23:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.15,0:23:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.86,0:23:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我以前就察覺到了\N聽說三鷹很討厭狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.40,0:23:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?果然是這樣嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.53,0:23:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.10,0:24:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「三鷹拼死特訓!\N怕狗還能談戀愛嗎」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.33,0:24:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,狗知道誰是牠的主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.17,0:24:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特訓就包在我們身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.05,0:24:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當我們互相凝視時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.45,0:24:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會有一道奇妙的旋律\N在心中迴響著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:33.30,0:24:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無法用言語來表達愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:40.27,0:24:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只好彈奏起了鋼琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:46.75,0:24:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請把夢丟進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.08,0:24:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為我測量一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:53.92,0:24:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛有多深
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:58.73,0:25:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用輕觸的嘴唇演奏著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:04.93,0:25:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平靜的合聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:11.90,0:25:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使擁抱著妳依然惆悵滿懷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:18.01,0:25:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夢見了Fantasy
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:25.08,0:25:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開啟了只有我們兩人\N才看得見的門扉Fantasy
